4. How to run the actual generation workflow manually right now

Before automating fully, you can run it manually.

For V1 or V2

Step 1

Open:

generation/v1/csr_study_design_generator.md or

generation/v2/csr_study_design_generator.md


Step 2

Replace:

{{SOURCE_TEXT}}

{{STRUCTURED_ELEMENTS}}

{{TARGET_DETAIL_LEVEL}}


with your actual case content.

Step 3

Paste that prompt into your LLM interface.

Step 4

Save the returned paragraph as:

generated_text.txt


---

