Step 1: planner

Open:

generation/v3/csr_study_design_planner.md

Fill in:

{{SOURCE_TEXT}}

{{STRUCTURED_ELEMENTS}}


Run it in the LLM.

Save the JSON output.

Step 2: generator

Open:

generation/v3/csr_study_design_generator.md

Fill in:

