6. How to run the batch workflow

Once your gold_standard/ folder has cases, run:

python scripts/batch_evaluate.py

This script should:

iterate through each case folder

load the files

call the evaluator

save outputs into batch_evaluation_outputs/


Expected outputs:

summary.csv

summary.json

per_case/*.json


Again, this becomes fully real only after the dummy client is replaced with a real one.


