7. How to run the A/B test

Once you have:

generation/v1/csr_study_design_generator.md

generation/v2/csr_study_design_generator.md


run:

python scripts/ab_test_generator_prompts.py

That should:

load each case

generate text with prompt A

generate text with prompt B

score both with the same evaluator

choose a winner

save CSV and JSON summaries


Outputs go into:

ab_test_outputs/


