9. What I would do right now in your position

I would run it in this order:

First

Do one case manually:

run V1

run V2

score both

compare outputs


Second

Do one V3 case:

planner

generator

scorer


Third

Once the prompts are behaving well, connect the Python harness to a real model.

That avoids wasting time debugging code before you know the prompts are good.


